## Overview

The OWON PC341-W-TY helps you monitor the amount of electricity consumed and produced in your facility by connecting the clamp onto the power cable. It monitors whole home energy and up to 2 individual circuits with bidirectional measurement capability, making it ideal for solar net metering applications.

## Key Features

- **Tuya Compliant** — fully compatible with Tuya Smart and Smart Life apps
- **Tap-to-Run & Automation** — supports automation with other Tuya devices
- **Single/3-Phase Compatible** — works with both single and three phase systems
- **Three CTs for Single Phase** — three current transformers for single phase application
- **Real-time Monitoring** — measures Voltage, Current, Power Factor, Active Power
- **Bi-Directional Measurement** — supports both energy consumption and production measurement
- **Residential & Commercial** — suitable for both home and business applications
- **Lightweight & Easy Install** — wall mounting with external antenna
- **Every 15s Reporting** — real-time data updates every 15 seconds

