| Sub CT | 2.5mm three-pole audio connector with 1m cable |

## Product Usage

The PC341-W-TY three phase energy meter connects via clamp-on CTs to monitor real-time power consumption and production. The external antenna design ensures reliable signal transmission even in shielded environments. Perfect for solar PV systems, home energy management, and commercial sub-metering.

